Title: SmartDocGuard: AI-Powered Document Curator

Idea Detail:
Use LLMs to scan documents for grammar, spelling, tonal imbalance, and contradictions to ensure polished and coherent writing.

Potential Benefits:
Enhances content quality, reduces human review effort, and prevents miscommunication or reputational risks from unintended tone or inconsistencies.

Proposed Solution:
Integrate an LLM-based module into writing platforms that highlights issues in real time and suggests context-aware edits with severity levels.